                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-456-18520405 t18520405-456-punishment-97"></join>Confined Two Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
